The paper deals with segmentation of medical images using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The specific application is in medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and the use of prior knowledge and adversarial learning techniques suggests an emphasis on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURAL).
